<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>FinanceCoach AI</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:#0f172a;
    color:white;
}

.container{
    max-width:1200px;
    margin:auto;
    padding:20px;
}

nav{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
    padding:20px 0;
}

.logo{
    font-size:24px;
    font-weight:700;
}

.btn{
    background:#22c55e;
    color:white;
    padding:12px 24px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:10px;
    cursor:pointer;
    text-decoration:none;
    font-weight:600;
}

.hero{
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:space-between;
    min-height:80vh;
    gap:60px;
}

.hero-left{
    flex:1;
}

.hero-left h1{
    font-size:4rem;
    line-height:1.1;
    margin-bottom:20px;
}

.hero-left p{
    font-size:1.2rem;
    color:#cbd5e1;
    margin-bottom:30px;
}

.hero-right{
    flex:1;
}

.dashboard{
    background:white;
    color:black;
    border-radius:20px;
    padding:25px;
    box-shadow:0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.25);
}

.card{
    background:#f1f5f9;
    padding:15px;
    border-radius:12px;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

.section{
    padding:100px 0;
}

.section-title{
    text-align:center;
    font-size:2.5rem;
    margin-bottom:50px;
}

.features{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
    gap:25px;
}

.feature{
    background:#1e293b;
    padding:25px;
    border-radius:16px;
}

.feature h3{
    margin-bottom:10px;
}

.waitlist{
    text-align:center;
}

input{
    width:100%;
    max-width:450px;
    padding:15px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:10px;
    margin-top:20px;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

footer{
    text-align:center;
    padding:30px;
    color:#94a3b8;
}

@media(max-width:768px){

.hero{
    flex-direction:column;
    text-align:center;
}

.hero-left h1{
    font-size:2.7rem;
}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<nav>
<div class="logo">FinanceCoach AI</div>
<a href="#waitlist" class="btn">Join Waitlist</a>
</nav>

<section class="hero">

<div class="hero-left">
<h1>Your AI Finance Coach</h1>

<p>
Upload your spending data and get personalized insights,
saving opportunities, and financial coaching in seconds.
</p>

<a href="#waitlist" class="btn">
Get Early Access
</a>
</div>

<div class="hero-right">

<div class="dashboard">

<h3>Monthly Insights</h3>

<div class="card">
💸 Food Delivery Spending: ₹6,400
</div>

<div class="card">
⚠️ 3 forgotten subscriptions detected
</div>

<div class="card">
📈 Potential savings: ₹2,750/month
</div>

<div class="card">
🎯 AI Recommendation:
Reduce dining out by 15% and save
₹11,500/year.
</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="section">

<h2 class="section-title">
Why Use FinanceCoach AI?
</h2>

<div class="features">

<div class="feature">
<h3>Smart Spending Analysis</h3>
<p>
See exactly where your money goes.
</p>
</div>

<div class="feature">
<h3>Subscription Detection</h3>
<p>
Find recurring charges you forgot about.
</p>
</div>

<div class="feature">
<h3>Personalized Advice</h3>
<p>
Receive AI-powered financial guidance.
</p>
</div>

<div class="feature">
<h3>Saving Opportunities</h3>
<p>
Discover ways to keep more money.
</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="section waitlist" id="waitlist">

<h2 class="section-title">
Join the Waitlist
</h2>

<p>
Be the first to try FinanceCoach AI.
</p>

<form>

<input
type="email"
placeholder="Enter your email"
required
>

<br>

<button class="btn">
Join Waitlist
</button>

</section>

<footer>
</footer>

</div>

</body>
</html>
